{"tid":858921,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係一食譚仔就生暗瘡?","createTime":"2018-10-12T06:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T06:47:51.000Z","uid":101972,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cf4f0510d1f162f017bff5ad58a9f16ee66fb738","tid":858921,"uid":101972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T06:51:10.000Z","msg":"以前中學幾乎日日都食譚仔，果陣塊面爛曬咁制。到而家戒左譚仔一段時間，就冇乜點生過暗瘡。不過有時間唔中食一餐譚仔，之後果幾日塊面又會開始黎料係咁出暗瘡。有冇人都係咁?<br />\n<br />\n利申：平時食開酸辣"},{"pid":"df49578a8309f1b2f69523cc1ca57a20d5e22035","tid":858921,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:42:26.000Z","msg":"味精"},{"pid":"2969874bc9b030e1e9bc135e5099962c823b4b22","tid":858921,"uid":205446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T02:40:16.000Z","msg":"我係一食肚痛"},{"pid":"7198d62af1b3df5365ea2e1b493d3b78e6bb8034","tid":858921,"uid":121701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T06:30:58.000Z","msg":"我一食南記就生"},{"pid":"c4fb33bea8c5cd40ede92db8fbd815bba17134e5","tid":858921,"uid":105590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T06:47:51.000Z","msg":"成日好撚想食 但一食就爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}